#### [MODIFY] [PersonSingleView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/PersonSingleView.tsx)

- **Mission Backlog / Active Protocol Headers**:
