  - New: `font-bold text-sm tracking-tight`
- **Instructional Labels**:
  - Current: `text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest`
  - New: `text-xs font-semibold`

---

### [Global] Design Principles
- **Title Case**: Switch from all-caps to Title Case for most descriptive headers and instructions.
- **Tracking**: Standardize on `tracking-tight` or default tracking for improved letter spacing readability.
- **Font Weight**: Move from `font-black` to `font-bold` for standard headers to avoid "blurring" at small sizes.

